== Overview ==
Based on the same design as the [[Cyclic Laser]], this advanced version uses a stronger beam. The ACL unfortunately uses significant amounts of reactor power to fire properly.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Advanced Cyclic Laser can be bought in the workshop after acquiring [[Radial Laser Technology]].
